data.message: Best Facebook Moment of 2010 from David Fraser of Orlando, FL: "My Facebook moment was on September 5, 2010. I had been sick since 4/9/2009 and on the liver transplant list for a while. On Sept 4, a FB friend asked me to remind her of what organ I needed…The next day I received the call and was given a life saving transplant. FB updates are why I am here today!" Read more and share your story at http://ow.ly/3qpJi.
